name: LineCake-A1
description:
LineCake is an exclusive model for your imagination.

It has a relaxed anime atmosphere, transmits calm and manages to take you to those places where you imagine.

As you can see, the prompts are very simple, they only describe details of how you want the scene to be.

You don't need to complicate the AI ​​just give it what you want to see.

With some prompts like (line art) you can get almost perfect results.

Version A1.

The sample photos are just a demonstration of a random place, give free rein to your creativity.
